# Technical Areas of Interest

My repositories are focused on several key areas of software engineering:

## Cloud-Native Applications

Applications designed to take advantage of Azure platform services and modern deployment models.

## Distributed Systems

Systems composed of independently deployable services communicating through APIs and messaging.

## Event-Driven Architecture

Architectures that use asynchronous messaging and events to improve scalability and resilience.

## Event Sourcing and CQRS

Systems that use business events as the source of truth while maintaining optimised read models.

## Platform Engineering and DevOps

Automation, deployment pipelines, infrastructure management, and operational excellence.

## AI-Assisted Development

Exploring practical uses of AI to improve software delivery and engineering productivity.

